Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.27,0:00:12.12,kanji,,0,0,0,,水面の波紋から　顔逸らしたのは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:17.77,kanji,,0,0,0,,私の心　揺らいだの隠したくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.77,0:00:24.11,kanji,,0,0,0,,あなたと並んでるだけの心臓が
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.11,0:00:28.42,kanji,,0,0,0,,火照りやまない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:31.53,kanji,,0,0,0,,酔い　吐息　はにかんで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:34.59,kanji,,0,0,0,,柔い夢を見て
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:37.44,kanji,,0,0,0,,袖触れて　満ち引いて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.44,0:00:40.42,kanji,,0,0,0,,目が合った
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.42,0:00:43.32,kanji,,0,0,0,,奥底のまぶしさを
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.32,0:00:47.03,kanji,,0,0,0,,一口味わうように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.03,0:00:52.88,kanji,,0,0,0,,名前を呼ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:01:00.51,kanji,,0,0,0,,喉通ったフレイバーには
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.51,0:01:06.40,kanji,,0,0,0,,初めて知る感情あふれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.40,0:01:15.13,kanji,,0,0,0,,あこがれも傷も全て　今
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:22.28,kanji,,0,0,0,,溶け込んで　光る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:30.93,kanji,,0,0,0,,グラスを透かしては　向こう側覗いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.93,0:01:36.91,kanji,,0,0,0,,流る雲を　目線でなぞるあなた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.91,0:01:42.67,kanji,,0,0,0,,世界が変わるほど綺麗だと思った
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:47.45,kanji,,0,0,0,,風吹く午後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:50.46,kanji,,0,0,0,,隣り合う　影と影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:53.64,kanji,,0,0,0,,そっと期待をして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.64,0:01:56.46,kanji,,0,0,0,,打ち消して　待ちあぐね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.46,0:01:59.46,kanji,,0,0,0,,手を取った
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.46,0:02:02.38,kanji,,0,0,0,,ほろ苦い　ほの甘い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.38,0:02:11.96,kanji,,0,0,0,,こぼれそうな想いが胸を満たす
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.62,0:02:19.58,kanji,,0,0,0,,あどけない瞳が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:25.33,kanji,,0,0,0,,熱を持ってかすかに惑う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:34.19,kanji,,0,0,0,,今日までの二人　全て　もう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.19,0:02:41.20,kanji,,0,0,0,,飛び越えそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:50.86,kanji,,0,0,0,,本音は曖昧なままでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.86,0:02:55.08,kanji,,0,0,0,,思ってまだ遠くない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:03:00.38,kanji,,0,0,0,,でもその涙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:04.88,kanji,,0,0,0,,理由を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:11.94,kanji,,0,0,0,,独り占めしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:20.93,kanji,,0,0,0,,喉通ったフレイバーには
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:26.82,kanji,,0,0,0,,初めて知る感情あふれ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:35.43,kanji,,0,0,0,,あこがれも傷も全て　今
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:42.80,kanji,,0,0,0,,溶け込んで　光る
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:45.80,kanji,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.27,0:00:12.12,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Mặt nước lay động sóng lăn tăn,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.27,0:00:12.12,vietsub - Sao chép,,0,0,0,,vội vàng ngoảnh mặt em quay đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:17.77,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Chỉ vì em muốn giấu đi,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:17.77,vietsub - Sao chép,,0,0,0,,cõi lòng mình đang rung động.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.77,0:00:24.11,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Chỉ cần bên cạnh người thôi,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.77,0:00:24.11,vietsub - Sao chép,,0,0,0,,chỉ riêng con tim này đã...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.11,0:00:28.42,vietsub,,0,0,0,,không ngừng nóng lên.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:31.53,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Hơi men say, nụ cười thẹn thùng.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:34.59,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Em mơ giấc mộng dịu êm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:37.44,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Tay áo ta khẽ chạm, gần rồi lại rời xa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.44,0:00:40.42,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Ánh mắt chạm nhau.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.42,0:00:43.32,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Sự rực rỡ từ tận sâu thẳm ấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.32,0:00:47.03,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Tựa như muốn nhấp môi nếm thử.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.03,0:00:52.88,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Em khẽ gọi tên người.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:01:00.51,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Trong hương vị vừa trôi xuống nơi cổ họng 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.51,0:01:06.40,vietsub,,0,0,0,,trào dâng bao cảm xúc lần đầu em biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.40,0:01:15.13,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Những khát khao cùng với những tổn thương,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.40,0:01:15.13,vietsub - Sao chép,,0,0,0,,ngay lúc này tất cả...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:22.28,vietsub,,0,0,0,,hòa quyện vào nhau và tỏa sáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:30.93,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Xuyên qua chiếc ly thuỷ tinh trong veo,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:30.93,vietsub - Sao chép,,0,0,0,,lặng lẽ em ngắm người phía bên kia .
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.93,0:01:36.91,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Người đang mải miết dõi theo,  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.93,0:01:36.91,vietsub - Sao chép,,0,0,0,, áng mây lửng lờ trên bầu trời.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.91,0:01:42.67,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Thật đẹp đến mức ngỡ như, 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.91,0:01:42.67,vietsub - Sao chép,,0,0,0,,thế giới này đang đổi thay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:47.45,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Buổi chiều gió lộng.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:50.46,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Ta kề bên nhau, như hình với bóng.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:53.64,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Em khẽ có chút hy vọng.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.64,0:01:56.46,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Rồi lại chối bỏ, rồi lại đợi chờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.46,0:01:59.46,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Em nắm tay người.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.46,0:02:02.38,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Nửa đắng nửa chát, nửa ngọt nửa ngào.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.38,0:02:11.96,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Tình cảm dâng trào lấp đầy lồng ngực em
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.62,0:02:19.58,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Đôi mắt ngây thơ của người,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:25.33,vietsub,,0,0,0,,nóng bừng lên và thoảng nét bối rối.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:34.19,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Giữa hai chúng ta đến hôm nay,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:34.19,vietsub - Sao chép,,0,0,0,,tất cả dường như...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.19,0:02:41.20,vietsub,,0,0,0,,sắp vượt ranh giới rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:50.86,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Lời thật lòng cứ để mập mờ cũng chẳng sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.86,0:02:55.08,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Vì em tin đôi ta chẳng còn cách xa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:03:00.38,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Thế nhưng những giọt lệ kia,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:04.88,vietsub,,0,0,0,,cùng với lý do...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:11.94,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Em muốn giữ cho riêng mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:20.93,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Trong hương vị vừa trôi xuống nơi cổ họng
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:26.82,vietsub,,0,0,0,,trào dâng bao cảm xúc lần đầu em biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:35.43,vietsub,,0,0,0,,Những khát khao cùng với những tổn thương,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:35.43,vietsub - Sao chép,,0,0,0,,ngay lúc này tất cả...
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.43,0:03:42.80,vietsub,,0,0,0,,hòa quyện vào nhau và tỏa sáng.
